column1: #     This table provides the list of input catalogues that have been used to select any given source that was analysed by the Gravitational Lens module and published in the lens candidate table.

column2: the catalogues considered for this selection are mostly external
column3: although sources identified by DPAC based on the classification performed by other processing have also been included here.
